<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='442000' id='t-442000'>So, OK, so why?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='444000' id='t-444000'>So we have the finger blasters. Other people have dinosaurs, you know.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447000' id='t-447000'>Why do we have them? Well, as I said,</span>
