<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='453000' id='t-453000'>But why is it important?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='455000' id='t-455000'>We use it in a pretty pragmatic way, to be honest.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='458000' id='t-458000'>We think playfulness helps us get to better creative solutions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463000' id='t-463000'>Helps us do our jobs better,</span>
