<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467000' id='t-467000'>Now, an adult encountering a new situation --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471000' id='t-471000'>when we encounter a new situation we have a tendency</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474000' id='t-474000'>to want to categorize it just as quickly as we can, you know.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='477000' id='t-477000'>And there’s a reason for that: we want to settle on an answer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483000' id='t-483000'>Life’s complicated; we want to figure out</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486000' id='t-486000'>what’s going on around us very quickly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='487000' id='t-487000'>I suspect, actually, that the evolutionary biologists</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='489000' id='t-489000'>probably have lots of reasons [for] why we want</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='491000' id='t-491000'>to categorize new things very, very quickly.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494000' id='t-494000'>One of them might be, you know,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='496000' id='t-496000'>when we see this funny stripy thing:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='497000' id='t-497000'>is that a tiger just about to jump out and kill us?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500000' id='t-500000'>Or is it just some weird shadows on the tree?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501000' id='t-501000'>We need to figure that out pretty fast.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='503000' id='t-503000'>Well, at least, we did once.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504000' id='t-504000'>Most of us don’t need to anymore, I suppose.</span>
</span>
</p>
