<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='506000' id='t-506000'>This is some aluminum foil, right? You use it in the kitchen.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='508000' id='t-508000'>That’s what it is, isn’t it? Of course it is, of course it is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='511000' id='t-511000'>Well, not necessarily.</span>
